title: CEO Jane Fraser Speaks at The Economic Club of Washington D.C.
tag-1: CEO Jane Fraser Speaks at The Economic Club of Washington D.C.
tag-2: Citi CEO Jane Fraser spoke to her confidence in the banking system during a fireside chat at the Economic Club of D.C. with David Rubenstein, co-chairman of The Carlyle Group and chairman of the Economic Club. She also discussed her career and vision for Citi’s future.
